messages.message:
<!here> We just got approvals for using Microsoft Azure Containers to test on Instabase.com (http://Instabase.com) and can begin testing once they send them over!

We can then figure out the next steps to be able to bring it to customers (which requires a call to Azure to send page counts). We can review the call out on what it takes to do and if we can report out on our own or some solution.

But for now we will get the containers and begin testing the services!
This is so so awesome! Thank you Matt for spearheading this effort! Im super exicted about getting my hands on these and hooking them up with our system!
This is awesome, great job making it happen!
